column5: Hey, Went to the river section of tobin lake saturday and sunday. Saturday, the fishing was slow, fished 12 hours, and caught 3 sauger and a walleye. Sunday, the fishing really picked up, and we caught 30 fish, a mix of walleye and sauger. Biggest fish of the trip was a 21 inch sauger. PikemanIf you need any info on tobin, please feel free to e-mail me.
